text.textblock: We certify that these regulations will not have a significant impact on a substantial number of small entities. Therefore, a regulatory flexibility analysis as provided in Public Law 96-354, the Regulatory Flexibility Act, is not required.
These regulations impose no additional reporting and recordkeeping requirements necessitating clearance by the Office of Management and Budget.
